    },
    {
      "id": "SurvivalAreaNorthHouse_Text_LookingForwardToVisitors",
      "en_US": [
        "I started living here where no one\n",
        "could reach me without using Rock Climb.\r",
        "I came because I got sick and tired of\n",
        "seeing people.\r",
        "But when I stopped seeing people,\n",
        "I began looking forward to visitors.\r",
        "Where one lives can change people and\n",
        "Pokémon, that’s what I’m saying."
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "SurvivalAreaNorthHouse_Text_ShardColorsEmphasize",
      "en_US": [
        "Red Shards emphasize power.\n",
        "Blue Shards are for special effects.\f",
        "Yellow Shards are for status problems.\r",
        "Red Shards are what I like!"
      ]
    }
